node.text:
Hailing from Tsukiji and managed by @watami.sg, @nikukappo.sg at ION Orchard offers authentic Japanese Kappo (割烹) style cuisine, and focus on the Meat category of menu. Niku Kappo satisfies different types of customers with the different unique and authentic meat dishes, together with the wide variety of menu items.⁣ ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣
𝐓𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐢𝐬 𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐥𝐲 𝐚 𝐅𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐲 𝐕𝐚𝐥𝐮𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐥𝐞 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐦𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧:-⁣⁣⁣
Buy 2, Get 2 Free! Buy any 2 Value Sets (u.p $8.90 to $14.90) And Get 2 free Budget Sets of your choice! (u.p $6.90) Comes with iced drink or miso soup! Swipe to see the menu. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Feature here are: ⁣⁣⁣
𝕍𝕒𝕝𝕦𝕖 𝕞𝕖𝕒𝕝:⁣⁣⁣
Salmon & Ikura Rice ⁣⁣⁣
Pepper Beef Rice⁣⁣⁣
𝔹𝕦𝕕𝕘𝕖𝕥 𝕞𝕖𝕒𝕝:⁣⁣⁣
Teriyaki chicken⁣⁣⁣
Roasted Mackerel ⁣⁣⁣
Iced milk tea⁣⁣⁣
Miso soup⁣⁣ ⁣
⁣

Whatsapp 87690496 to place your order! ⁣
For nearby location, $3 per delivery or free delivery with minimum spend of $30 (before GST). ⁣
For islandwide delivery, $8 per delivery, or free delivery with minimum spend of $60 (before GST). ⁣
Or order and pick up via drive-through service. ⁣⁣⁣⁣ ⁣
Thank you @sghappens @nikukappo.sg for sending these delicious meal over. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
📍 ℕ𝕚𝕜𝕦 𝕂𝕒𝕡𝕡𝕠 𝕀𝕆ℕ 𝕆𝕣𝕔𝕙𝕒𝕣𝕕⁣ ⁣⁣⁣
